{"tid":1213524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中國澳門市正式成立］澳門立法會加裝國徽","createTime":"2019-06-13T01:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:45:36.000Z","uid":10014,"like":16,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"2c27d1e5999f3f15ba2b0ba3cf48a6f09a2315d6","tid":1213524,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kSKpHsR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkSKpHsR.png&h=b3155e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉自正報<br />\n立會加裝國徽 (07/06/2019)<br />\n<br />\n話根據六月一日生效的新修改《關於使用國旗、國徽、區旗、區徽及奏唱國歌的具體規定》行政法規，近期多個機構都加裝國徽，立法會自然不能「例外」喎。<br />\n<br />\n除立會大樓外牆加裝一個國徽，大樓內的全體議會大廳也同樣裝上大大的國徽。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日澳門，明日香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d8d05117516380d90079464dbcd5f7209cc91fbe","tid":1213524,"uid":196924,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"維尼咁搞根本冇可能收回台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cdd3bf04e70562e22162fd6ca483314149526c","tid":1213524,"uid":50328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f62643f444d8ca714f5c2d8952b6c56f49519e2f","tid":1213524,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"858caae4f478f9ad118b2e446f0808488f7b79e2","tid":1213524,"uid":163758,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"f62643f444d8ca714f5c2d8952b6c56f49519e2f","tid":1213524,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"澳門係真係好多支那人"},{"pid":"33cd5dccedd412aa41c2516abe6d9d15260879c5","tid":1213524,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ea2ab6b6aade6a24e7